Package models

Class CommitteeMember

java.lang.Object
models.User
models.Student
models.CommitteeMember
public class CommitteeMember extends Student
The CommitteeMember class represents a committee member in CAMs. Committee Member have a unique ID, password, name, faculty and points. Each Committee Member also has a Role which determines their level of access.
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
Chin Jun Hao, Mark

      Constructor used for importing CommitteeMember from CSV.
      Parameters:
      userID - The user ID of the Committee Member.
      password - The password of the Committee Member.
      name - The name of the Committee Member.
      faculty - The faculty to which the Committee Member belongs.
      registeredCamps - The list of camps the Committee Member is registered for.
      enquiries - A map containing the Committee Member's enquiries, with camp names as keys and lists of enquiry IDs as values.
      facilitatingCamp - The name of the camp facilitated by the Committee Member.
      suggestions - A list of suggestion IDs representing suggestion provided by the Committee Member.
      points - The points earned by the Committee Member.
